remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="520ca-104">它可能不太方便，若要重新命名方法參數為 WMI 用戶端提供使用者易記的名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="520ca-104">It might be inconvenient to rename method parameters to present WMI clients with more user-friendly names.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="520ca-105">這個屬性可讓您指派 WMI 的使用者易記名稱，同時保留您現有的內部命名慣例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="520ca-105">This attribute lets you assign user-friendly WMI names while retaining your existing internal naming conventions.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="520ca-106">在下列範例中，整數參數就內部而言，保持 「 i 」，但會以 WMI 用戶端公開為 「 值 」。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="520ca-106">In the following example, the integer parameter remains i internally, but will be exposed as "The Value" to WMI clients.</span></span>  
  
```  
[ManagementTask]  
static public int PrintValue([ManagementName("The Value")]int i)  
{  
   Console.WriteLine("The Value is {0:x}", i);  
   return i;  
}  
```
